Package: thesisdown
Title: An updated R Markdown thesis template using the bookdown package
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Chester", "Ismay", email = "chester.ismay@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut")),
    person("Nick", "Solomon", email = "nick@nicksolomon.me", role = "aut"),
    person("Kuoyuan", "Cheng", role="aut"))
Description: Based on ismayc/thesisdown. Using the bookdown package and
    LaTeX thesis template from University of Maryland, College Park,
    this package aims to encourage reproducible research using simple
    Markdown syntax while embedding all of the R code to produce plots
    and analyses as well.
Maintainer: Kuoyuan Cheng <yourself@somewhere.net>
